TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed AutoCompleteType extends System.Enum

summary.span: 表示控制 控件中自动完成功能的行为的值。

span.span: Represents the values that control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature in a control.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 若要帮助进行数据输入，Internet Explorer 5 和更高版本以及某些其他浏览器支持名为自动完成的功能。To assist with data entry, Internet Explorer 5 and later and some other browsers support a feature named AutoComplete. 记忆式键入功能监视的文本框中，并将存储在用户输入的值的列表。AutoComplete monitors a text box and stores a list of the values that the user has entered. 当用户返回文本到另一个时，将显示值的列表。When the user returns to the text box another time, the list of values is displayed. 而不是重新键入一个值，用户可以直接从此列表中选择值。Instead of retyping a value, the user can simply select the value from this list. > [!NOTE] > 并非所有浏览器支持记忆式键入功能。Not all browsers support the AutoComplete feature. 请与你的浏览器来确定兼容性。Check with your browser to determine compatibility. 若要控制的自动完成功能的行为控件中，使用属性。To control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature for a control, you use the property. 枚举用于表示可以将应用于值属性。The enumeration is used to represent the values that you can apply to the property. 默认情况下属性控件设置为`AutoCompleteType.None`。By default, the property for a control is set to `AutoCompleteType.None`. 使用此设置，控件与其他共享列表具有相同控制跨不同的页。With this setting, the control shares the list with other controls with the same across different pages. 你还可以共享列表之间控件基于类别而不是基于。You can also share a list among controls based on a category instead of based on an . 当您将设置属性设置为其中一个类别值 (如`AutoCompleteType.FirstName`或`AutoCompleteType.LastName`)，则所有具有相同类别的控件共享相同的列表。When you set the property to one of the category values (such as `AutoCompleteType.FirstName` or `AutoCompleteType.LastName`), all controls with the same category share the same list. 可以禁用自动完成功能通过设置控件属性设置为`AutoCompleteType.Disabled`。You can disable the AutoComplete feature for a control by setting the property to `AutoCompleteType.Disabled`. 请参阅浏览器文档有关配置和启用自动完成功能的详细信息。Refer to your browser documentation for details on configuring and enabling the AutoComplete feature. 例如，若要启用自动完成功能在 Internet Explorer 版本 5 或更高版本，从**工具**菜单中，选择**Internet 选项**。For example, to enable the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer version 5 or later, from the **Tools** menu, choose **Internet Options**. 然后选择**内容**选项卡。选择**记忆式键入功能**按钮可查看并修改记忆式键入功能的选项。Then choose the **Content** tab. Choose the **AutoComplete** button to view and modify options for the AutoComplete feature. 有关在 Internet Explorer 中自动完成功能的详细信息，搜索[HTML 窗体中使用自动完成](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp)上的 MSDN Library 中http://msdn.microsoft.com/library。For more information on the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer, search for [Using AutoComplete in HTML Forms](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp) in the MSDN Library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library. ## Examples 下面的示例演示如何使用枚举来指定的记忆式键入功能类别控件。The following example demonstrates how to use the enumeration to specify the AutoComplete category for a control. > [!IMPORTANT] > 此示例具有一个接受用户输入的文本框，这是一个潜在的安全威胁。This example has a text box that accepts user input, which is a potential security threat. 默认情况下，ASP.NET 网页验证用户输入是否不包含脚本或 HTML 元素。By default, ASP.NET Web pages validate that user input does not include script or HTML elements. 有关详细信息，请参阅[脚本侵入概述](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07)。For more information, see [Script Exploits Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07).
